 Dike  
 ♫  Completely blind (Completely blind)  ♫

609
00:53:57,990 --> 00:53:59,820
 Hello, Your Honor! 

610
00:53:59,820 --> 00:54:01,970
 I'm a huge fan! 

611
00:54:01,970 --> 00:54:03,390
 You're so cool! 

612
00:54:03,390 --> 00:54:05,190
 That man is a total psycho. 

613
00:54:05,190 --> 00:54:07,260
 I used to work part-time in a department store parking lot. 

614
00:54:07,260 --> 00:54:10,120
 I was so angry and resentful. 

615
00:54:10,120 --> 00:54:13,160
♫  Oh oh oh in my place  ♫

