00:54:13,160 --> 00:54:18,710
♫  And drink the rest (And drink the rest) from drought to  ♫

617
00:54:18,710 --> 00:54:21,040
I wasn't too bad, right?

618
00:54:22,290 --> 00:54:25,820
♫  That's my very own inner evergreen 
