619
00:54:25,820 --> 00:54:28,310
 Is it okay to accept this? 

620
00:54:28,310 --> 00:54:30,170
 You did well. 

621
00:54:30,810 --> 00:54:32,790
 Thank you. 

622
00:54:51,340 --> 00:54:54,870
Are you saying we've really been putting on a show?

623
00:54:54,870 --> 00:54:56,820
A show?

624
00:54:58,450 --> 00:55:01,100
I don't care if you criticize me,

625
00:55:01,100 --> 00:55:04,660
but you can't call our trial a fake.

626
00:55:04,660 --> 00:55:09,010
It's an insult to many people who mustered up their courage.

627
00:55:09,010 --> 00:55:11,890
We only helped to get the first word out,

628
00:55:11,890 --> 00:55:15,690
but without the courage of those people, nothing could have been done.

629
00:55:16,920 --> 00:55:20,200
- I'm sorry, I'm a little late. 
 - Hello.

630
00:55:21,460 --> 00:55:23,130
Thank you.

631
00:55:23,810 --> 00:55:28,660
It's nice to meet you. I work at Metropolitan Investigation Unit, I'm Jo Min Seong.

632
00:55:28,660 --> 00:55:32,380
 I talked to the team leader, but his reaction was so weird. He was annoyed. 

633
00:55:32,380 --> 00:55:36,510
 He's the one who got mad, when you said you were digging into Kang Yo Han, right? 

634
00:55:38,330 --> 00:55:41,460
- You must be Su Hyeon's team leader. 
 - Yes.

635
00:55:41,460 --> 00:55:44,620
Yun Su Hyeon seems delicate but she does her work well.

636
00:55:44,620 --> 00:55:47,290
Sometimes she can be overzealous, though.

637
00:55:47,290 --> 00:55:50,710
Is my chief taking good care of you?

638
00:55:50,710 --> 00:55:52,410
Excuse me?

639
00:55:52,410 --> 00:55:57,090
Money is definitely a powerful motivation for anyone.

640
00:55:57,090 --> 00:56:00,180
Judge Kim, don't pretend to be smart.

641
00:56:00,180 --> 00:56:01,900
Did I say something wrong?

642
00:56:01,900 --> 00:56:06,220
Do you know why I'm helping Judge Kang?

643
00:56:06,860 --> 00:56:08,600
Why?

644
00:56:09,280 --> 00:56:12,310
In the household disinfectant case,

645
00:56:12,960 --> 00:56:15,610
I lost my baby daughter.

646
00:56:15,610 --> 00:56:18,200
I'd been defending a large company all my life,

647
00:56:18,200 --> 00:56:22,450
but once I became a victim, I felt a little lost.

648
00:56:23,240 --> 00:56:25,330
You surely know the outcome of that case, right?

649
00:56:25,330 --> 00:56:28,010
You know what the judgment was too.

650
00:56:28,010 --> 00:56:29,700
Lawyer Go ...

651
00:56:29,700 --> 00:56:31,910
Don't call me a lawyer anymore.

652
00:56:31,910 --> 00:56:36,470
I already betrayed my client, and now I'm not a lawyer anymore,

653
00:56:36,470 --> 00:56:38,640
I'm just a criminal.

654
00:56:38,640 --> 00:56:44,080
When all this is over, I'll pay for my crime.

655
00:56:46,510 --> 00:56:51,020
This girl  was sexually harassed while she was drunk.

656
00:56:51,020 --> 00:56:55,860
She had to just watch the perpetrator get released on probation.

657
00:56:56,590 --> 00:56:59,080
The judge said

658
00:56:59,080 --> 00:57:03,010
"The offender is a promising medical student and should be treated leniently."

659
00:57:03,010 --> 00:57:05,520
Then, what about me?

660
00:57:05,520 --> 00:57:07,840
Are you telling me to live with it

661
00:57:07,840 --> 00:57:10,680
because I don't have much of a future?

662
00:57:17,090 --> 00:57:22,680
Jo Min Seong's older sister, worked at the Saerim Department Store.

663
00:57:22,680 --> 00:57:26,270
My sister was the head of the family and had to take care of her brother,

664
00:57:26,270 --> 00:57:28,930
so she worked without taking any days off.

665
00:57:28,930 --> 00:57:31,760
Until the moment the department store

666
00:57:31,760 --> 00:57:35,590
started having cracks, made sounds, and eventually collapsed.

667
00:57:35,590 --> 00:57:39,910
How was the sentence in that case, Judge?

668
00:58:18,270 --> 00:58:20,360
Judge Oh!

669
00:58:25,980 --> 00:58:29,260
You’re a chairwoman now, right?

670
00:58:29,260 --> 00:58:32,650
I heard that you were also in charge of the operation support group of our live court.

671
00:58:32,650 --> 00:58:36,220
I don't even have the ability, but I've been entrusted with a lot of tasks.

672
00:58:39,420 --> 00:58:43,390
I understand that there are a lot of problems

673
00:58:43,390 --> 00:58:46,880
in our foundation.

674
00:58:46,880 --> 00:58:48,460
I'll try to change all that.

675
00:58:48,460 --> 00:58:51,060
I'll cut off all ties with the politicians and conglomerates,

676
00:58:51,060 --> 00:58:55,600
and focus on those in need. Back to our beginnings.

677
00:58:56,300 --> 00:58:59,360
Yes, it won't be easy.

678
00:58:59,360 --> 00:59:02,250
If there's anything I can do to help you, feel free to let me know.

