Oh my! No, no, if you do this, I'll get in trouble.

699
01:00:51,400 --> 01:00:54,090
This is costume jewelry. For dressing up.

700
01:00:57,100 --> 01:00:59,000
Dressing up.

701
01:01:00,700 --> 01:01:02,650
You should be friendly,

702
01:01:02,650 --> 01:01:08,920
but when you're on stage, don't miss a single moment to overpower everyone.

